Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.34,paper,,0,0,0,,{\pos(377,129)}第十
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.34,paper,,0,0,0,,{\pos(367,157)}大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.34,paper,,0,0,0,,{\pos(316,181)}雨过天晴心和畅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.34,paper,,0,0,0,,{\pos(319,302)}欲照山樱日影长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.34,paper,,0,0,0,,{\pos(370,324)}运势
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,第十六签
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦  折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今年看来会有好事发生呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你是抽到末吉了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20}末吉：一般而言，是除了凶以及大凶以外最不好的签
